
Ranger Help for: enemy goat
===========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing goat means your Ranger knows how to hunt goats, rams, ibex, and
similar sure-footed horned animals.

This is most thematic for mountains, hills, forests, plains, and jungles.
It fits Rangers who know cliffs, ridges, and rocky grazing paths.

COMMAND:
  setenemy goat

=============================================================================
